#  Descriptive Analytics & Exploratory Data Analysis (EDA)

This folder contains datasets and code dedicated to **Exploratory Data Analysis (EDA)** and identifying patterns within historical data. These materials serve as the foundational **"analysis of results"** required for both high-level academic instruction and professional research consultation [2, 3].

###  Methodology & Key Objectives
*   **Pattern Recognition:** Identifying critical trends and behaviors within complex datasets to support **organizational planning**.
*   **Data Integrity:** Cleaning and preparing raw data to ensure accuracy in the **analysis of results** .
*   **Visual Storytelling:** Transforming complex statistical outputs into "clear, compelling narratives" for stakeholders.
